{"tid":1004531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍將親自拍片向中國拜年  日媒：實屬罕見！","createTime":"2019-02-01T13:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T15:11:19.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"88279e23fcf55e39e6e6e597774873fe33bdb548","tid":1004531,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕農曆春節將至，據日媒指出，日首相安倍晉三將會親自拍攝賀年短片向中國拜年，並形容此舉實屬罕見，也被視為是在為中國國家主席習近平之後訪日的行程安排暖身。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpZPmLQV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpZPmLQV.jpg&h=9f36453c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安倍晉三去年10月訪中，中日關係和緩，今天農曆新年將拍攝一段賀年短片向中國拜年。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，本月5日將是農曆豬年新年第一天，在日本國內雖然沒有過春節的習俗，但今年有意親自錄製一支賀歲短片直接向中國人民拜年，以顯示穩固中日關係的決心，日媒紛紛表示這次以影片向中國賀歲的方式非常罕見<br />\n<br />\n向來關係緊繃的中日兩國，自去年10月安倍晉三的訪中行程結束後，習近平也預計於今年6月出訪日本，顯示中日雙方關係開始回暖。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2690469\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2690469&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=59e84931\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2690469&h=8f02a8fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2690469</a>"},{"pid":"f72b5e651e9c536b470cd5f50dda1b6d59f0a141","tid":1004531,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T13:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係恭喜你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af8c090628f860bea6060d4ade3028af47e7b0c","tid":1004531,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T13:36:44.000Z","msg":"贈興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544e99a36de95b4a7541ce93cd58f76aceddd798",